<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.10">
<l>mañcu lāmaṇi māṭaṅkaḷ cūḻtiru veḷḷaṟai yataṉmēya</l>
<l>vañca ṉampurai yuntiru vuruvaṉai yātiyai yamutattai</l>
<l>nañcu lāviya vēlvala vaṉkali kaṉṟico laiyiraṇṭum</l>
<l>eñca liṉṟiniṉ ṟēttaval lārimai yōrkkara cāvarkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these five-[times]-two verses of Kalikaṉṟi,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one skilled with a spear where poison swirls,</l>
<l>To always praise without error the primal [Lord], [our] nectar,</l>
<l>The one whose divine form resembles kohl, who dwells in Tiruveḷḷaṟai</l>
<l>Encircled by jeweled mansions where mist swirls,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will be rulers of the unblinking [celestials].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
